---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About GoldPriceNepal.online | Nepal's Trusted Gold Price Source"
  description="Learn about GoldPriceNepal.online — Nepal's trusted platform for live gold and silver prices, powered by daily FENEGOSIDA rate updates."
  canonical="https://www.goldpricenepal.online/about"
>
  <div class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        About <span class="text-yellow-600">GoldPriceNepal.online</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-5 text-gray-600">
        <p class="text-lg">
          GoldPriceNepal.online is Nepal's dedicated platform for tracking live gold and silver prices.
          We provide accurate, up-to-date pricing data sourced daily from FENEGOSIDA — the Federation of
          Nepal Gold &amp; Silver Dealers Associations.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          We believe every Nepali should have free access to accurate precious metal prices. Whether
          you're a jeweller, investor, or consumer planning a purchase, our platform provides the
          transparency you need to make informed decisions.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">What We Offer</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li>Daily gold prices for 24K, 22K, and 18K per tola and gram</li>
          <li>Silver prices per tola and gram</li>
          <li>Historical price charts (1 day to 1 year)</li>
          <li>Gold weight and value calculator</li>
          <li>USD/NPR currency converter</li>
          <li>Market news and analysis</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Data Source</h2>
        <p>
          All gold and silver rates are sourced from <strong>FENEGOSIDA</strong> (Federation of Nepal
          Gold &amp; Silver Dealers Associations), the official body responsible for setting precious
          metal prices in Nepal. Rates are typically announced each morning and are valid for the
          trading day.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          The prices displayed on this website are for informational purposes only. While we strive
          to provide accurate and timely data, we cannot guarantee that prices match exact market
          rates at any given moment. Always verify with your local jeweller or FENEGOSIDA before
          making any purchase or sale.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For inquiries, corrections, or partnership opportunities, please reach out to us at
          <a href="mailto:info@goldpricenepal.online" class="text-yellow-600 hover:underline">
            info@goldpricenepal.online
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
